headline: Shares of Jack Dorsey’s Block Jump 8.5% on S&P 500 Inclusion
summary: Inclusion in the S&P 500 index will increase Block's visibility and exposure to institutional investors, who will indirectly gain exposure to bitcoin.

headline: Chevron’s Victory in the Oil-Patch Brawl Was a Much-Needed Win
summary: The acquisition of Hess—and its stake in a generational oil find—helps clear up lingering doubts about Chevron’s growth prospects.
